{"type": "article", "id": 30985, "title": "你见过会发光的“棒棒糖”吗？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-08-14T23:07:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 31484, "name": "Agnes Felt"}, {"id": 31485, "name": "Boris Klimek"}, {"id": 22980, "name": "LASVIT"}, {"id": 31486, "name": "Dreamfarm"}, {"id": 31487, "name": "Clara Schweers"}, {"id": 31488, "name": "Aliaksei Malevich"}, {"id": 31489, "name": "Thomas Coward"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 156, "image": "img/article/article_show/201608142330512R4VhNIJrPe0ztfq.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Saitens by Clara Schweers</h3><p>这张颇具未来感的极简双人座椅 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/41531835/Saitens\" rel=\"nofollow\">Saitens</a> 是德国设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/claraschweers\" rel=\"nofollow\">Clara Schweers</a> 的作品，两个座位间的联系看似紧密同时又巧妙地避免了直接的身体接触，Schweers 希望通过这种微妙的距离感探索人与人之间的沟通。她的灵感来源于达芬奇的三张手稿，启发最大的一张描绘了阳光射向抛物线镜面后反射出的光线。整张座椅呈对称结构，座位分别朝向两侧，优美的曲面则由独立的高强度钓鱼线穿插交织而成。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233352WimEqkOjSRhI2cLC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233352QSbai63yeTDBYC82.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.105134\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233351f9pxJN1qMXw6SlEG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233352GZzMSjNbBoC70y3q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233353MIFhygPQjvoAxDLS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608142333500DeqwrQ7mabXKd3i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.591687\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Spadle by Dreamfarm</h3><p>你有没有想过长柄勺和铲子也能二合一？Dreamfarm 的这款名为 Spadle 的厨具有一根非常灵活的手柄，只要扭转顶端的两个关节就能够在汤勺和铲子之间随意切换。Spadle 的头部采用柔软的硅胶制刷头，可以轻松地刮取锅中的事物，表面还设计了几个常用的刻度，为烹饪提供了极大的便利。这是它的<a href=\"https://dreamfarm.com/spadle/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 19.95 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233418qoC5hg29ASUBDbrx.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562222\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233415oMUHVWvECu76FKSQ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562874\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233414Y8DxAQ2cmG6fBlpk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.522455\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608142334158QCmTNsEFkDiq10Z.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562874\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233416old1ExwO9Z4KLctW.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562874\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233414Ma0GE7x8w2JAyBok.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562874\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lavolta Carry Case by Aliaksei Malevich</h3><p>假如你需要背着 iMac 上街该怎么办？这个罕见的难题一度困扰着设计师 Aliaksei Malevich，有一次他不得不带着自己的 iMac 出席一个重要的会议，正是这段经历启发他设计了 iMac 专用的便携包 Lavolta Carry Case。它由羊毛毡和皮革手工制成，不仅可以容纳下 27 寸 Thunderbolt 显示器，还有独立的口袋用来放置键盘等配件。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Lavolta-Carrying-Case-Apple-27-inch/dp/B01GQDBLFM\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 55.49 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233325czgLAJHKtIyw4kX2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233324hLglZC6rPbpWSVBq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233324fI1ES7pOXceZ8ozj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608142333246tjX7OsFA1JpdT9K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.776667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233324Ka7iBZk8hlAcEbqJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.455333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016081423332529cXU6rd4ARjJDZH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Cat bed by Agnes Felt</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/AgnesFelt\" rel=\"nofollow\">Agnes Felt</a> 是一个来自立陶宛的品牌，专门经营手工制成的羊毛毡制品。旗下的猫窝都围绕着猫咪为主题打造，比如顶部凸起的“猫耳”、猫脸造型的入口，甚至还有连树叶和枝梢上的鸟窝都如实还原的树型猫窝，看起来都非常可爱。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/AgnesFelt/items?section_id=13169506\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>订购，售价从 99 美元到 390 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233230VqA4luG81i2Xt0yf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.819298\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233230Qh12qIiBoPdEsY3K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.775439\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233231LPMBrkzn97FRAZKW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.871930\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233231uBCX0FyrQEmgaRcd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.763158\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608142332309uvYwPqOme51MLjE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233231WcKlLDqHITriPARt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.194737\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>MOTIF by Thomas Coward Studio</h3><p><a href=\"http://thomascoward.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Thomas Coward</a> 设计的这款 <a href=\"http://thomascoward.com/filter/products/MOTIF\" rel=\"nofollow\">MOTIF</a> 洗手台看起来有些中规中矩，实际上却利用各种细节展示出水与光之间优美的互动。圆柱形的水盆和台面之间通过铬合金下水器连接，造成一种悬浮效果。由蚀刻玻璃制成的盆底上印有各式花纹，当光线穿透时就会在洁净的台面上倒映出精美的图案，带给人舒适的视觉感受。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233158q2B0O7WatH8Zbh3X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.901087\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608142331590rtnVpbWQUeJ3GAZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.790217\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233158Jbvk1g40wQ9tyZj7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.444565\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233159SJ4V0aht18j92GNn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.383696\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233158cf3dKgm2GA0RMJEH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233159bnauPON6ME72x0IJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lolipop by Boris Klimek</h3><p>还记得透过有色玻璃瓶窥见的世界是什么样的吗？斯洛伐克设计师 <a href=\"http://www.borisklimek.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Boris Klimek</a> 为 <a href=\"http://lasvit.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lasvit</a> 设计的 <a href=\"http://lasvit.com/milan-2016/lights/lollipop--317/video\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lollipop</a> 灯具系列或许会让你回忆起那种多彩而有趣的体验。这些吊灯和台灯由形状不规则的有色玻璃板、金属支架以及嵌在内部的光源构成，看上去就像是把棒棒糖放在太阳下一样。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233108bxNvw1MGIUkVFjEl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233108G6ipUEu3CjkhyzSL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.743750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160814233108OIwiQCBJM2FEGarY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.345000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}